{"tid":1472503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"置頂精華-我要㩜炒：希望各位能比壓力各國領事要求cut大陸出生人士廁板免簽證","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:08:22.000Z","uid":172633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d54dddee2e6fc4ea72d53e75d380056e9d0c1d9a","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"各位親愛的連登仔女,<br />\n<br />\n 有一點大家都知道的事係：絕大多數的支那蝗以每日150隻的極速湧入香港，根本係為左7年後攞永居後轉藍色廁所板免簽證到世界各地以支那蝗的思想去作出破壞其他國家文化的行為（如隨地大小便），甚至破壞其他國家國家安全（如孟晚舟）。<br />\n<br />\n但此安排應排除9771後出生港人（因為他們的思想和行為至少同97前香港人相同）。<br />\n<br />\n所以為了杜絕一切的惡行，要求各國領事能以下行政命令方法取消所有在9771或之後獲簽發身份證明書由內地扺港人士的藍色廁板免簽證待遇，以保純正香港人在外地的聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n一個好例子：以色列同阿拉伯世界國家實施敵對政策，互相禁止對方國民入境，甚至過境轉機也禁止<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有無其他更好建議可以集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哈哈，<br />\n支那人你地都係共享大灣區的榮耀la,<br />\n咪留係香港獻世，想7年後洗底，唔洗旨意呀屌你</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：純屬學術討論，並非鼓勵或鼓吹任何歧視思想或違法或暴力行為"},{"pid":"75c621edcc8f87d9142a866c37b62f13c6a42222","tid":1472503,"uid":270979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"細節上唔可行 , 除非港共政府配合 !"},{"pid":"a534f7eb45cfbf8a9decd6c722391f74865d2ef0","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75c621edcc8f87d9142a866c37b62f13c6a42222","tid":1472503,"uid":270979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"細節上唔可行 , 除非港共政府配合 !"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"係無錯<br />\n<br />\n咁就各國領事館落行政指令方式要求他們的移民局嚴格執行有關政策<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲正呀，繞過港共政府</span>"},{"pid":"1c267a0b2a07cdaf8691f71d475490afb016f1d2","tid":1472503,"uid":107572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a534f7eb45cfbf8a9decd6c722391f74865d2ef0","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75c621edcc8f87d9142a866c37b62f13c6a42222","tid":1472503,"uid":270979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"細節上唔可行 , 除非港共政府配合 !"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"係無錯<br />\n<br />\n咁就各國領事館落行政指令方式要求他們的移民局嚴格執行有關政策<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲正呀，繞過港共政府</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"絕對要！咪俾班仆街影衰我哋香港人"},{"pid":"e8f29509c25e0893ff49fe3b09cd037d86428f10","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c267a0b2a07cdaf8691f71d475490afb016f1d2","tid":1472503,"uid":107572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a534f7eb45cfbf8a9decd6c722391f74865d2ef0","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75c621edcc8f87d9142a866c37b62f13c6a42222","tid":1472503,"uid":270979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"細節上唔可行 , 除非港共政府配合 !"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"係無錯<br />\n<br />\n咁就各國領事館落行政指令方式要求他們的移民局嚴格執行有關政策<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲正呀，繞過港共政府</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"絕對要！咪俾班仆街影衰我哋香港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"大家準備好寫信比各國喇，首先目標係日韓星馬泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e688bda10e5fd625e1d832b7f246413432cddb1b","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8f29509c25e0893ff49fe3b09cd037d86428f10","tid":1472503,"uid":172633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c267a0b2a07cdaf8691f71d475490afb016f1d2","tid":1472503,"uid":107572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a534f7eb45cfbf8a9decd6c722391f74